flowchart LR
  Users[Corporate and Remote Users] --> Entra[Microsoft Entra ID / Microsoft 365]
  Users --> Edge[HQ Firewall and VPN]
  Edge --> Core[Core Switching]
  Core --> UserVLAN[User VLAN]
  Core --> ServerVLAN[Server VLAN]
  Core --> MgmtVLAN[Management VLAN]
  ServerVLAN --> AD[AD DS / DNS / DHCP]
  ServerVLAN --> File[File Services]
  ServerVLAN --> Monitor[Monitoring]
  Edge --> Tunnel[Site-to-Site VPN]
  Tunnel --> AWS[AWS VPC]
  AWS --> Public[Public Subnets]
  AWS --> Private[Private Subnets]
  Private --> EC2[EC2 Application Servers]
  EC2 --> CW[CloudWatch / Systems Manager]
  Entra --> Intune[Intune Endpoint Management]
